Package divisor

Class IntPair

  • java.lang.Object
    • divisor.IntPair
  • class IntPair
extends java.lang.Object
    This class holds integers in specified pairs.

    This allows for safe movement between classes and storage in ArrayLists.

    Author:
    Dalton
